(Overview) Tj
T*
(Machine learning is a branch of AI where systems improve using data.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Learning Objectives) Tj
T*
(- Explain the meaning of Machine Learning in Computer Science using accurate subject) Tj
T*
(vocabulary.) Tj
T*
(- Describe the key ideas behind training data, patterns, prediction, and models.) Tj
T*
(- Apply Machine Learning to examples such as using past examples to predict a new) Tj
T*
(outcome.) Tj
